                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Loomis</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Leistiman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-08-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Loomis states that the United States European Squadron has been ordered to
                    Beirut.)</p>
